<section class="about">
  <div class="wrap-sm">
    <p class="eyebrow">About This Effort</p>
    <h2 class="section-h">Who We Are</h2>
    <p>
      The Montavilla Community Land Trust is a neighbor-led coalition organizing to permanently
      protect the land at 7700 SE Stark Street through community ownership. We are residents,
      market vendors, and local business people who believe that Montavilla's most important
      gathering place should belong to the people who built it.
    </p>
    <p>
      We are in the early stages of formal organization. We welcome neighbors with experience
      in law, nonprofit finance, real estate, design, organizing, and community outreach to
      join the steering committee.
    </p>
    <p>
      Contact us at <a href="mailto:info@montavillalandtrust.org">info@montavillalandtrust.org</a>
      or follow <strong>#MontavillaLandTrust</strong> for updates.
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:0.85rem; color:rgba(122,158,126,0.6); margin-top:2rem; font-family:'Crimson Pro',serif; font-style:italic;">
      This coalition operates independently from the Montavilla Farmers Market organization.
